  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Clean and slice mushrooms into small pieces.",
    "In a mixing bowl, combine almond milk, agar agar powder, flax seeds meal, coconut oil, soy sauce or tamari, garlic powder, paprika, salt, and pepper. Mix until well combined.",
    "Add sliced mushrooms to the mushroom mixture and stir gently until coated evenly with the spice mixture.",
    "Transfer the mixture into a greased dish and bake for 30 minutes in preheated oven.",
    "Remove from oven and let it cool slightly before serving."
